    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp with razor-sharp throttle response via six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is complemented by a recently serviced M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including a reinforced rear subframe, rod bearing replacement, and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis remains taut with original aluminum suspension components and zero oxidation. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the factory finish retains its deep luster, free of imperfections. A mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning collector.",
